Package org.osate.aadl2.modelsupport.adapter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExternalModelAdapter
    This adapter can be attached to Aadl Object Models Its role is to keep a reference to a Java object of a model that is external to the AADL model.
    ExternalModelAdapterFactory
    This class implements an ExternalModelAdapter factory: It attaches an adapter that handles an external model reference.
